  "title": "Project Manager (Door Specialist)",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities</p><ul><li>Manage the day-to-day operations on projects undertaken by the company.</li><li>Oversee and manage projects to ensure timely completion and to achieve highest quality of works or site.</li><li>Maintain project control systems, planning, scheduling and to manage projects within manpower budgets and by the company.</li><li>Plan and organize resources to achieve higher productivity and minimize wastages and float time.</li><li>Assist in other business activities as and when assigned.</li></ul><p>Requirement</p><ul><li>Candidate must possess at least\n     Diploma/Advanced/Higher/Graduate Diploma, Bachelor's Degree/Post Graduate\n     Diploma/Professional Degree in Engineering (Civil) or equivalent.</li><li>At least 8 Year(s) of working experience in the Construction field is required for this position.</li><li>Preferably Manager specialized in Engineering - Civil/Construction/Structural or equivalent.</li><li>Specialize in Sub-Contractor works.</li></ul>",
