    "description": "<p>TRUSSCO PTE LTD, a leading and well accomplished specialist manufacturer and sub-contractor serving the construction industry for nearing 30 years locally.</p><p><br /></p><p>Our products include commercial grade metal doors and ironmongery, security/detention metal doors, security locks and hardware, auto-sliding doors and gates, safety padding system and many others.</p><p><br /></p><p>We are always searching out for talented and experienced professional and executives to fill the posts needed to meet the business growth.</p><p><br /></p><p>Our office is located at Bulim Square.</p>",
